<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 08:12:51 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>奶奶泡泡的婚礼</title><link>https://some.pics/69ef1a80cee93</link><description>&lt;p&gt;泡泡奶奶的婚礼&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="
A photograph of three people standing together indoors. In the centre is an elderly woman wearing a white lace wedding dress, a small tiara, and a veil, with a purple rose corsage pinned to her chest. She is smiling warmly. To her left stands a tall young man in a light blue button-up shirt and dark pants, also smiling. To her right stands another young man in a teal button-up shirt and dark pants, wearing a watch. The setting appears to be a simply furnished room with beige walls. The photo has the warm, slightly faded quality of a film photograph." height="3204" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/brennan/69ef1a80cee93.jpg" width="2154"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://brennan.some.pics"&gt;@brennan&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 08:12:51 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>蜜蜂乘船</title><link>https://some.pics/69eeb57ee2b07</link><description>&lt;p&gt;蜜蜂！在船上！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="a minecraft screenshot of a bee in a boat" height="470" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/fady/69eeb57ee2b07.png" width="482"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://fady.some.pics"&gt;@fady&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 01:01:53 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>树干</title><link>https://some.pics/69ee57f691d85</link><description>&lt;p&gt;树干&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Sunlit mixed forest with moss-covered pine trunk in foreground and shallow woodland pool reflecting light among spring foliage" height="1080" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/esamecar/69ee57f691d85.jpg" width="1620"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://esamecar.some.pics"&gt;@esamecar&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 18:22:49 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>淡蓝柔光</title><link>https://some.pics/69ee4b245b585</link><description>&lt;p&gt;柔和的蓝色。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Forsythe branches in front of blue sky." height="4624" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/69ee4b245b585.jpg" width="2604"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 17:28:07 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>怀念好兄弟Nutekit</title><link>https://some.pics/69ee34a7dd1a5</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Nutekit是我哥哥的萨路基猎犬。他曾是个好孩子，我们会想念他的。安息吧，我们的王子❤️&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Nutekit is my brother's saluki. He was a good boy, and he will be missed. Rest well our prince ❤️" height="1598" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/b00ksc0ut/69ee34a7dd1a5.jpg" width="1008"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://b00ksc0ut.some.pics"&gt;@b00ksc0ut&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 15:52:10 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>